{"id":125861,"type":6,"name":"盛裝舞步愛作戰","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/e7/34/125861_Kpezo.jpg","summary":"　　Ben（洪卓立饰）与Michelle(卫诗雅饰）早于小学时已是欢喜冤家，中学时在旋转木马上开展了一段朦胧的盛夏初恋。二人其后因一次误会及信任不足而以为对方背叛自己，再在旋转木马上一刀两断。 \r\n　　几年后，已升读大学的两人在“马术研习班”上重遇，更结识了不修边幅的阿谦（罗钟谦饰）、爽朗的Boy(赵蔚欣饰）、千金小姐Kimmy（关婉珊饰）和娘娘腔的Nel（陈家乐饰）。经过重重考验后，六人由初时的男女恶斗变成知心好友，Boy与Nel、阿谦与Kimmy更发展成恋人。Ben与Michelle虽表面与对方貌合神离，但心底里却是余情未了。马术训练即将结束，他们能否跨越障碍，再次走在一起？","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>盛装舞步爱作战</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期六 23:00-23:30</li><li><span>监制: </span><a href=\"/person/17494\">錢國偉</a></li><li><span>主演: </span>詩雅、<a href=\"/person/17493\">洪卓立</a>、<a href=\"/person/17319\">陳家樂</a>、趙碩之、<a href=\"/person/16873\">羅仲謙</a>、關婉珊、林威辰、<a href=\"/person/17462\">龔嘉欣</a>、<a href=\"/person/16561\">許志安</a>、Mandy Lieu</li><li><span>别名: </span>Dressage To Win</li><li><span>集数: </span>9（香港）／5（大馬）</li><li><span>开始: </span>2008-06-14</li><li><span>结束: </span>2008-08-03</li><li><span>类型: </span>時裝偶像</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>香港</li><li><span>电视台: </span>TVB</li><li><span>主题歌演出: </span>Phoenix Yeung、Iris Wu《一步一傾心》</li><li><span>制作年份: </span>2008年5月至2008年7月</li><li><span>编审: </span>徐家祥</li>","collection":{"collect":2},"tags":[{"name":"TVB","count":1},{"name":"2008","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":483489,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/483489","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":483490,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/483490","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":483491,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/483491","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":483492,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/483492","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":483493,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/483493","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":48